Example of Use|Example of use:
Card Charge transactions that are acquired from the Merchants by the Acquiring Bank and forwarded to the Issuing Banks through Card Clearing are periodically settled (generally once a day). |||CR Card Financial Settlement Procedure Instance Record|Card Financial Settlement Procedure Instance Record|||||The card financial settlement procedure refers to a specific instance of the execution of the settlement process|IO|IO|||||||O||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||#|Listed Semantic API Descriptions
